14. [출제의도] 대화의 특정 정보 파악하기
W: Welcome to Nihao Chinese Language School. 
May I help you?
M: I’d like to register for the beginner course 
starting in December. How much is it?
W: The beginner course is 80 dollars. And we’re 
giving a 10% discount to new applicants who 
register by this weekend.
M: Wow! I’m lucky! Is there any other discount? 
W: Yes, there’s a 5% discount for adults over the 
age of 40 to celebrate our 40th anniversary.
M: I’m over 40. Can I get a 15% discount then?
W: No. You can choose either of the two. I’ll give 
you the higher discount.
M: I’d like the 10% one, of course. Is the 
textbook included in the tuition fee?
W: No. You should buy it at a bookstore.
M: Alright. Here’s my credit card.
