your job there?
M: I take orders now, but the manager said I’ll 
learn to make coffee next week.
W: That’s a great opportunity. I wish I could 
work in a coffee shop, too.
M: Really? My boss is looking for one more 
part­time worker.
W: Great. Can you check if it’s still open?
M:                                          
19. [출제의도] 대화의 적절한 응답 고르기
