M: Oh, yes. She was the star of the show.
W: Is she going to audition to be a model for this 
year’s fashion show?
M: I don’t think so. She’s a senior, so she’s very 
busy looking for a job.
W: Hmm... She could be a perfect model for our 
town festival. I can’t remember what you did 
at last year’s festival.
M: I took care of the stage lighting in last year’s 
play.
W: That’s wonderful. Can you be the lighting 
director for the fashion show?
M: I don’t see why not. I’m in. 
W: Great. We’ll be a good team.
12. [출제의도] 대화의 특정 정보 파악하기
