movies such as a thief, police officer, 
scientist, and more. 
W: This role requires singing as well as acting.
M: That’s why we need him. He did a musical a 
few years ago. 
W: Well, then we have the perfect actor for our 
movie.
M: I bet he won’t disappoint us.
